{
  "stem": "16313.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can see through these things, through the holes, that the Russian army passed by.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was other people over there, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who can remember people hiding?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was hiding, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And they walking, and the Russian army take it over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's done.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When this all settled down, I tried to go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I go [INAUDIBLE] back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I go back to Poland through the Bug River, and I see what the Germans do to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in the Warsaw, and see the-- my-- the-- my father, [HEBREW], work on the streets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he got the [? beard, ?] a beard, and some German pass by, knock him off [? with the-- ?] this over the head, with the-- with the-- with the-- with this [? carbine ?] they got.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- Then I run back the other side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I see this terrible story, go back to-- on the Russian side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got on ?] the way, but it's no use.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I see what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I see, I must-- I must do something to help myself and save my life, because I see what happened over there [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was on the Russian side, and the Russian side, start a new story.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The rest of a family was in the ghetto, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put them all in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I got some ideas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People passing by the borders, I know they was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They suffer, and the ghetto was overcrowded with people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People dying of hunger, of all kind of things, diseases.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they put on a half a million people in a couple streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they put on the wall, and [? that's ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
